data.title: Latest news and headlines from Australia and the world

data.text:
Pilot who crashed into Cairns hotel identified

The pilot who was killed when he crashed into a hotel in Cairns has been identified.

36 minutes ago02:29

Residents living west of Melbourne feel forgotten

Residents living in Melbourne’s fast-growing outer western suburbs are feeling the squeeze as the wait continues for promised transport upgrades.

2 hours ago02:20

Lamborghini Huracan, cash, jewellery seized in alleged drug bust across Queensland

A Lamborghini Huracan, cash and jewellery are among the luxury items seized in alleged drug bust across Queensland.

2 hours ago01:34

Donald Trump interviewed by Elon Musk

Former President Donald Trump was interviewed by Elon Musk on social platform ‘X', but it didn’t all go to plan.

Attempt to ban pokies on Anzac day fails as NSW parliament rejects proposal

An attempt to ban poker machines being played on Anzac Day in NSW has failed after the government and opposition rejected the proposed amendment.

Car slams into Sydney shop

A woman has climbed out of the wreck of her car after it crashed into a truck, then slammed straight through a shop at Granville.

Pressure ramps up on Labor to ban gambling ads

The federal government says the status quo on gambling in Australia is "untenable" as pressure ramps up on Labor to introduce a total ban on gambling advertisements.

2 hours ago01:42

Accused killer police officer has appeared in court.

Accused killer police officer Beau Lamarre-Condon has appeared in court over the alleged murders of Sydney couple Jesse Baird and Luke Davies.

Private sector wages sluggish as salaries grow 4.1 per cent in June

Wage growth in the private sector has seen its smallest quarterly increase since 2021.

Family 'devastated' after business destroyed by suspicious inferno in Dandenong

A family has been left 'devastated' after a business was destroyed by a suspicious inferno in Dandenong.

Investigations are ramping up to determine the identity of the pilot who crashed a stolen helicopter into a Cairns hotel.
